<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="S" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Source" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Source,</orth> spring, origin, first cause: <cit><quote>great floods have flown from simple --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. aww 2.1.143" default="NO" valid="yes">All's II, 1, 143</bibl></cit>. <emph>blow it</emph> (the cloud) <cit><quote>to the s. from whence it came,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 5.3.11" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C V, 3, 11</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>quell the s. of all erection,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tim 4.3.164" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. IV, 3, 164</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. mac 2.3.104" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. II, 3, 104</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 1.1.106" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. I, 1, 106</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 2.2.55" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 2, 55</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 3.13.160" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. III, 13, 160</bibl>. In <bibl n="shak. per 4.3.28" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. IV, 3, 28</bibl> M. Edd. <emph>--s,</emph> O. Edd. <emph>courses.</emph>
